rows.label: qst00100101_msg0001
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Right clear! Left clear!
Front clear! Goldmund
security, no problems, mo!

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0002
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]...But Kebikebi's shift
has a problem, mo!

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0003
rows.name:
When the time comes, Rimurimu
is supposed to take over
security here, but...

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0004
rows.name:
Rimurimu is over 3821 seconds late,
mo! This is the 1000th time, mo!

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0005
rows.name:
It's also the 1000th time
Kebikebi will miss dinner, mo...

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0006
rows.name:
I want to find Rimurimu and lecture
him from sunset to sunrise, but...

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0007
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Kebikebi can't search while on
guard duty, mo! I'm sleepy, mo!
My tummy is rumbling, mo!!

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0008
rows.name:
Momo?! You'll help me, mo?
Thank you, thank you, mo...

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0009
rows.name:
Then please find Rimurimu and tell
him it's time to change shifts, mo.

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0011
rows.name:
The reason he's late is
usually because Rimurimu
is watching salvaging...

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0101
rows.name:
If he's slacking off and
watching salvaging, he should
be on the Salvage Deck, mo.

rows.label: qst00100101_msg0102
rows.name:
If there's a reason,
Kebikebi won't be angry,
mo! I have a big heart, mo!
